Author: LELAND
Vol / Page: 68
Edition:
Quote: <i>school dental clinic</i>: At most large schools, and for each collection of small ones, there is a small prefabricated building set slightly apart in which you can find one or more School Dental Nurses who do all of the preventive, and most of the corrective dental work (free) for the children in their schools. The children, unlike you and I?, consider a visit to the SCHOOL DENTAL CLINIC an unpleasant necessity, at best. Hence the name
